<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>193</hymn_number>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Baibal Cathiang, Pathian Bia, A sung bik ro thil kei ca, Ka semnak a
 ka chimh i, Zei ka si a ka cawnpiak.

[V2]
 Ka vahvaih tik mawh-chiattu, Khamhtu dawtnak hmuh-saktu, A ka hruaitu
 le vengtu, Dantat maw laksawng pe tu.

[V3]
 Ramcar chung ngaihchiat sifah, Khuaruah har hnangam tertu, Mi nih
 thihnak tei khawhnak, Zumhnak nung a hmuhsaktu.

[V4]
 A ra laimi lawmhnak le, Misual dantatnak chimtu; Maw a sung bik Cauk
 Thiang, A sung bik ro thil kei ca.</lyrics>
<title>BAIBAL THIANG, CAUK THIANG CH193</title>
</song>